T1  - ‘Secret’ buy-backs of LDC debt
AU  - Cohen, Daniel
AU  - Verdier, Thierry
JO  - Journal of International Economics
VL  - 39
IS  - 3
SP  - 317
EP  - 334
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/11/01/
