T1  - How trade-related are intellectual property rights?
AU  - Maskus, Keith E.
AU  - Penubarti, Mohan
JO  - Journal of International Economics
VL  - 39
IS  - 3
SP  - 227
EP  - 248
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/11/01/
